0: SELECT MAX("Percent (%) Eligible Free (K-12)") FROM frpm WHERE "County Name" = 'Alameda';	----- bird -----	california_schools
1:
SELECT "School Name", "Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)"
FROM frpm
WHERE "School Type" = 'Continuation'
ORDER BY "Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)" ASC
LIMIT 3;	----- bird -----	california_schools
2: SELECT "Zip" FROM schools WHERE "County" = 'Fresno' AND "Charter" = 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
3:
SELECT s."MailStreet"
FROM frpm f
JOIN schools s ON f."CDSCode" = s."CDSCode"
ORDER BY f."FRPM Count (K-12)" DESC
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
4:
SELECT "Phone" 
FROM "schools" 
WHERE "Charter" = 1 
AND "FundingType" = 'Directly funded' 
AND "OpenDate" > '2000-01-01';	----- bird -----	california_schools
5:
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM satscores
JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools."CDSCode"
WHERE "AvgScrMath" > 400 AND schools.Virtual = 'Y';	----- bird -----	california_schools
6:
SELECT s."School"
FROM satscores ss
JOIN schools s ON ss.cds = s."CDSCode"
WHERE ss."NumTstTakr" > 500 AND s."Magnet" = 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
7:
SELECT s."Phone"
FROM satscores ss
JOIN schools s ON ss.cds = s."CDSCode"
ORDER BY ss."NumGE1500" DESC
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
8:
SELECT s."NumTstTakr"
FROM satscores s
JOIN frpm f ON s.cds = f."CDSCode"
ORDER BY f."FRPM Count (K-12)" DESC
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
9:
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM satscores s
JOIN schools sc ON s.cds = sc."CDSCode"
WHERE s."AvgScrMath" > 560 AND sc."FundingType" = 'Directly funded';	----- bird -----	california_schools
10:
SELECT f."FRPM Count (Ages 5-17)"
FROM satscores s
JOIN frpm f ON s.cds = f."CDSCode"
ORDER BY s."AvgScrRead" DESC
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
12:
SELECT MAX("Percent (%) Eligible Free (Ages 5-17)") 
FROM frpm 
WHERE "CDSCode" IN (
    SELECT cds 
    FROM satscores 
    WHERE CAST("NumGE1500" AS FLOAT) / "NumTstTakr" > 0.3
);	----- bird -----	california_schools
13:
SELECT s."Phone"
FROM satscores ss
JOIN schools s ON ss.cds = s."CDSCode"
ORDER BY ss."NumGE1500" DESC
LIMIT 3;	----- bird -----	california_schools
14:
SELECT s."NCESSchool", f."School Name", f."Enrollment (Ages 5-17)"
FROM frpm f
JOIN schools s ON f."CDSCode" = s."CDSCode"
ORDER BY f."Enrollment (Ages 5-17)" DESC
LIMIT 5;	----- bird -----	california_schools
15:
SELECT dname, AVG("AvgScrRead") AS avg_reading_score
FROM satscores
JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools."CDSCode"
WHERE schools."StatusType" = 'Active'
GROUP BY dname
ORDER BY avg_reading_score DESC
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
16:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM satscores 
WHERE cname = 'Alameda' AND NumTstTakr < 100;	----- bird -----	california_schools
17:
SELECT sname, "Charter School Number", "AvgScrWrite"
FROM satscores
JOIN frpm ON satscores.cds = frpm."CDSCode"
WHERE "AvgScrWrite" > 499
ORDER BY "AvgScrWrite" DESC;	----- bird -----	california_schools
18:
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM satscores
JOIN schools ON satscores.cds = schools."CDSCode"
WHERE schools.County = 'Fresno' AND schools.FundingType = 'Directly funded' AND satscores."NumTstTakr" <= 250;	----- bird -----	california_schools
